00:04:24.380 --> 00:04:26.920
to be done here.

00:04:26.920 --> 00:04:29.810
So moving on, once you get the
app going-- and I'm going to

00:04:29.810 --> 00:04:31.290
do that on my phone as well--

00:04:31.290 --> 00:04:34.230
but you can see here straight
