lot of similarities in what

00:27:13.830 --> 00:27:15.310
I'm asking for here.

00:27:15.310 --> 00:27:18.180
So for the first app-- for
Sleep as Android--

00:27:18.180 --> 00:27:20.410
think about a more standard
action bar, simpler

00:27:20.410 --> 00:27:22.270
navigation, standardized
settings.

00:27:22.270 --> 00:27:23.850
And just make the whole
thing easy to

00:27:23.850 --> 00:27:26.140
understand and get started.

00:27:26.140 --> 00:27:30.720
For Sleep Recorder, I think,
again, you kind of need a

00:27:30.720 --> 00:27:33.320
little bit of a UI overhaul.

00:27:33.320 --> 00:27:34.840
It doesn't need to be completely
redesigned.

00:27:34.840 --> 00:27:37.030
I'm not saying that you
shouldn't be using a

00:27:37.030 --> 00:27:38.050
