00:27:38.050 --> 00:27:39.990
I think that adds a
certain simplicity

00:27:39.990 --> 00:27:42.310
that works quite well.

00:27:42.310 --> 00:27:45.260
But I found it really hard to
understand how to get going.

00:27:45.260 --> 00:27:47.300
And I think that's something
that could really benefit and

00:27:47.300 --> 00:27:50.280
