engagement, particularly

00:27:50.280 --> 00:27:53.380
things around the
modal dialogs.

00:27:53.380 --> 00:27:55.510
As soon as you find that you
need to tell your users that

00:27:55.510 --> 00:27:57.980
they're doing something wrong,
that's usually a pretty clear

00:27:57.980 --> 00:28:01.150
indication that perhaps you
haven't created it in a way

00:28:01.150 --> 00:28:02.840
that they find intuitive.

00:28:02.840 --> 00:28:04.550
And overall, just make the
whole thing easier to

00:28:04.550 --> 00:28:05.670
understand.

